  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is Bum Bum Monsterz</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/1be47be57cc2d362686221d0a1f0674d.poster.avif?t=1734437594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/1be47be57cc2d362686221d0a1f0674d.webm?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/1be47be57cc2d362686221d0a1f0674d.mp4?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bum Bum Monsterz is a 2v2 to 4v4 team-based multiplayer party game! You can gather your friends for hilarious challenges, tackle obstacles, and solve puzzles. </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/87e2c0ed167d7c84112b3f426a356d8a.poster.avif?t=1734437594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/87e2c0ed167d7c84112b3f426a356d8a.webm?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/87e2c0ed167d7c84112b3f426a356d8a.mp4?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You and your friends can duke it out  in various team-based mini-games. </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/e142f7789ec8c41e48d861f1f045dbac.poster.avif?t=1734437594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/e142f7789ec8c41e48d861f1f045dbac.webm?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/e142f7789ec8c41e48d861f1f045dbac.mp4?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team play is always at the forefront in Bum Bum Monsterz's playgrounds. Teamwork makes the dreamwork.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/ca625c6ba6385980eb0ed55a2f3ae683.poster.avif?t=1734437594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/ca625c6ba6385980eb0ed55a2f3ae683.webm?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/ca625c6ba6385980eb0ed55a2f3ae683.mp4?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sometimes these playgrounds can become a little bit… well… Chaotic! But that’s the fun of it!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/6dbcfb93d03b54d42cf0aa0dbf6f871a.poster.avif?t=1734437594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/6dbcfb93d03b54d42cf0aa0dbf6f871a.webm?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/6dbcfb93d03b54d42cf0aa0dbf6f871a.mp4?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>But ultimately it’s about winning and taking the crown!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/693180e90de46eff5ac601c3da38ba49.poster.avif?t=1734437594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/693180e90de46eff5ac601c3da38ba49.webm?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/693180e90de46eff5ac601c3da38ba49.mp4?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And it’s about winning in style!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/bcba81258da23ed63c6785355bf57dd2.poster.avif?t=1734437594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/bcba81258da23ed63c6785355bf57dd2.webm?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/bcba81258da23ed63c6785355bf57dd2.mp4?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And maybe a little bit about… REVENGE!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/12371c46ddc59eb70fb2d8e04947c3fe.poster.avif?t=1734437594\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/12371c46ddc59eb70fb2d8e04947c3fe.webm?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071400/extras/12371c46ddc59eb70fb2d8e04947c3fe.mp4?t=1734437594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>So get ready to party with Bum Bum Monsterz</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
